FBIS4-14560 "drsov063_b_94011" FBIS-SOV-94-063 Daily Report 1 Apr 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Rumyantsev, Boldyrev, Others Create `People's Alliance' Rumyantsev, Boldyrev, Others Create `People's Alliance' MK0104100094 Moscow SEGODNYA in Russian 1 Apr 94 p 1 MK0104100094 Moscow SEGODNYA Russian BFN [POSTFACTUM report: "`People's Alliance' Patriotic Movement Created"] [Text] A group of political figures came forward yesterday with a statement about the creation of a new Russian patriotic movement, the "People's Alliance." One of the movement's masterminds, Dmitriy Olshanskiy, has said that preparations for its establishment have been in progress since early January. The statement reads: "We come forward with an initiative to unite the patriotic intelligentsia, all citizens of Russia. We consider as the paramount task the shaping of a policy and tactics of national reconciliation." The document is signed by Sergey Glazyev, Dmitriy Olshanskiy, Oleg Rumyantsev, Yuriy Boldyrev, and others.
